org.agreement_technologies.common.map_planner

Interface Plan

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    HPlan, IPlan
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    POPIncrementalPlan

    public interface Plan
    Basic interface of partial-order plans: extended by IPlan and HPlan and implemented by service.map_Planner.POPIncrementalPlan.
    Since:
    1.0
